        "text": "European Consumers should not be subjected to misleading marketing practices or unfair contracts. Such market practices are not only against the interests of individual consumers and households but also result in unfair competition. Finance Sweden therefore recognize and support regulations ensuring clear and relevant information enabling consumers to make informed choices and exercise their rights, as well as transparent contract terms balancing the interests of consumers and EU businesses.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s1",
          "section_path": [
            "EC Public Consultation on the Digital Fairness Act – Finance Sweden response"
