          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 9009,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "As there is legislation forbidding such dark patterns already in practice, there should be little or no use in introducing new legislation, as this would lead to unnecessary complexity where new legislation is introduced where there already are existing rules.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s2",
