          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 10240,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Regarding financial services, recent amendments to the Consumer Rights Directive imposing member states to forbid at least one of three specific dark patterns does not expand the protection but rather empathise on it. For financial services such practices mentioned as contractual issues in the consultation are included in the amendments of the Consumer Rights Directive.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s2",
          "section_path": [
            "Dark patterns, reactive design and issues with digital contracts."
          ],
          "span": null,
          "chunk_quality": "ok",
