          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 9397,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "The examples of unfair marketing relating to prices in the consultation are all examples of what is already considered to be misleading for consumers and in breach with the EU legislation on unfair market practices. Further legislation to prevent those practices should not be necessary.",
